---
layout: layouts/standard.njk
title: "Travel Journal — Cavero Diego"
description: "Places that shape us, textures we borrow."
section: viaje
footerOmit: viaje
lang: en
langBtn: true
pageStyle: |
  /* ─── Base ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  body { background: #E8E5DC; }

  /* ─── Archive header ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .viaje-archive-header {
    padding: 22vh 8vw 6vh;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(42,50,41,.08);
  }
  .viaje-archive-eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif;
    font-size: .58rem;
    letter-spacing: .32em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(42,50,41,.35);
    margin-bottom: 2.4rem;
  }
  .viaje-archive-title {
    font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 5vw, 4.8rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -.03em;
    line-height: .95;
    color: #2A3229;
  }

  /* ─── Empty state ────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .viaje-archive-empty {
    padding: 16vh 8vw;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 1.8rem;
  }
  .viaje-archive-empty-label {
    font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif;
    font-size: .58rem;
    letter-spacing: .32em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(42,50,41,.28);
  }
  .viaje-archive-empty-text {
    font-family: 'Boska', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(42,50,41,.35);
    max-width: 28ch;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  /* ─── Responsive ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .viaje-archive-header { padding: 18vh 6vw 5vh; }
  }
---

<header class="viaje-archive-header">
  <span class="viaje-archive-eyebrow">Cavero Diego · Travel Journal</span>
  <h1 class="viaje-archive-title">Travel<br>Archive</h1>
</header>

<main class="viaje-archive-empty">
  <span class="viaje-archive-empty-label">Coming Soon</span>
  <p class="viaje-archive-empty-text">
    The first journey is yet to be written.<br>
    Places that shape us, textures we borrow.
  </p>
</main>
